highlights.text: “Cabelos Brancos” by Léo Foguete is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #163.
Grupo Menos É Mais has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #1.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 913 days straight.
“Cachaçada - Ao Vivo” by Kaique e Felipe and Clayton & Romário is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 54 spots at #109.
